      "content": "**Connect** is the Powerhouse host application that serves as a container for all Powerhouse apps and drives. It provides:\n\n- A runtime environment for document editors and drive apps\n- Document drive management (local and remote drives)\n- Integration with Vetra Studio (the builder platform)\n- Built-in Tailwind CSS for styling\n- Document toolbar with standard actions (save, share, navigation)\n\nConnect is launched via `ph connect` (legacy) or accessed through `ph vetra --watch` (recommended). It typically runs at `http://localhost:3000/`.\n\nIn the context of development, Connect/Vetra provides a live preview environment where editors update dynamically as you make changes to the code.",
